long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
View geotagged photos in Google Drive. Mark location of your photos!!
Show off your favorite photos to the world, securely and privately show content to your friends and family.
Enjoy your photos being placed on a world map in a fascinating way. Drive PhotoMap helps you finding and visiting beautiful or important locations again.
You can select photo, image files from Google Drive. 

*What is a Geotagging?
Geotagging (also written as GeoTagging) is the process of adding geographical identification metadata to various media such as a geotagged photograph, websites, SMS messages, RSS feeds and is a form of geospatial metadata.
This data usually consists of latitude and longitude coordinates.
